data.description: All brick 3 bedroom/3 bath home in sought after Whitehall neighborhood, close to everything!  Fully ADA compliant with removable front ramp and updated bath w/wheelchair access.  Elegant formal living room with french doors, formal dining rm.  Spacious great room with brick fireplace.  Kitchen has large eat-in area with wall of windows overlooking huge deck with handicap ramp, and nice fully fenced backyard with shed/workshop.
